 "It was a dark and stormy night...",
 "The old mansion loomed ahead...",
 "The forest was dense and foreboding...",
 "The silence was deafening...",
 "The chill in the air was bone-chilling...",
 "The moon was full and blood-red...",
 "The fog rolled in like a thick blanket...",
 "The creaking of the floorboards echoed through the house...",
 "The howling of the wind made it impossible to think..."
 };

